<%- contentFor('body') %>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="page-hero-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="page-title">Our Approach</h1>
      <p class="page-description">A systematic methodology to transform your data into strategic wealth</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-wave">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,32L60,37.3C120,43,240,53,360,53.3C480,53,600,43,720,42.7C840,43,960,53,1080,53.3C1200,53,1320,43,1380,37.3L1440,32L1440,100L1380,100C1320,100,1200,100,1080,100C960,100,840,100,720,100C600,100,480,100,360,100C240,100,120,100,60,100L0,100Z" fill="#f8f9fa"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Approach Overview -->
<section class="approach-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="overview-grid">
      <div class="overview-content" data-aos="fade-right">
        <h2>Data-Driven Decision Making</h2>
        <p class="lead">Our approach combines technical expertise with business acumen to unlock the full potential of your data.</p>
        <p>At Revelate Operations, we believe that effective data strategy goes beyond technology. It requires a deep understanding of your business objectives, industry dynamics, and organizational culture. Our comprehensive approach addresses all aspects of data management, from collection and storage to analysis and activation.</p>
        <p>We focus not just on what the data shows, but on what actions it should drive. Our goal is to help you make informed decisions that lead to measurable business outcomes, whether that's increased revenue, improved efficiency, or enhanced customer experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-image" data-aos="fade-left">
        <img src="/assets/images/approach-illustration.png" alt="Data-Driven Approach" width="500" height="400">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Core Principles -->
<section class="principles-section bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Core Principles</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">The fundamental beliefs that guide our work</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="principles-grid">
      <div class="principle-card" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="principle-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Business-First Approach</h3>
        <p>We start with your business objectives and work backward to determine the right data strategy, ensuring all technical solutions directly support your goals.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="principle-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="principle-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-puzzle-piece"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Holistic Integration</h3>
        <p>We view your data ecosystem as an interconnected whole, ensuring that all systems and processes work together seamlessly to provide a unified view of your business.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="principle-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="principle-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Measurable Results</h3>
        <p>We define clear KPIs and metrics at the outset of every engagement, ensuring that all our work delivers quantifiable value and ROI for your business.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="principle-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="principle-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-users-cog"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>User-Centered Design</h3>
        <p>We design solutions with the end user in mind, focusing on adoption, usability, and practical application to ensure your team embraces the tools we implement.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Methodology -->
<section class="methodology-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Methodology</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A proven framework for transforming your data operations</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="methodology-timeline">
      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Phase 1: Discover</h3>
          <div class="timeline-grid">
            <div class="timeline-description">
              <p>We conduct a comprehensive assessment of your current data landscape, including systems, processes, and pain points. This phase includes:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Stakeholder interviews and workshops</li>
                <li>System and data audit</li>
                <li>Process flow mapping</li>
                <li>Gap analysis and opportunity identification</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-image">
              <img src="/assets/images/discover-illustration.svg" alt="Discovery Phase" width="300" height="200">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Phase 2: Strategize</h3>
          <div class="timeline-grid reverse">
            <div class="timeline-image">
              <img src="/assets/images/strategize-illustration.svg" alt="Strategy Phase" width="300" height="200">
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-description">
              <p>Based on our findings, we develop a tailored roadmap that aligns with your business objectives. This phase includes:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Data strategy development</li>
                <li>Technology stack recommendations</li>
                <li>Roadmap creation with clear milestones</li>
                <li>ROI projections and business case formulation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Phase 3: Implement</h3>
          <div class="timeline-grid">
            <div class="timeline-description">
              <p>We execute the plan using agile methodologies to ensure quality and minimize disruption. This phase includes:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>System configuration and customization</li>
                <li>Data migration and integration</li>
                <li>Process automation and workflow design</li>
                <li>User training and change management</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-image">
              <img src="/assets/images/implement-illustration.svg" alt="Implementation Phase" width="300" height="200">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Phase 4 -->
      <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Phase 4: Optimize</h3>
          <div class="timeline-grid reverse">
            <div class="timeline-image">
              <img src="/assets/images/optimize-illustration.svg" alt="Optimization Phase" width="300" height="200">
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-description">
              <p>We continuously refine and enhance your solution based on feedback and evolving needs. This phase includes:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Performance monitoring and KPI tracking</li>
                <li>User adoption assessment</li>
                <li>Iterative improvements and enhancements</li>
                <li>Ongoing support and knowledge transfer</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Transform Your Data Operations?</h2>
      <p class="cta-description">Let's discuss how our approach can help you achieve your business goals.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-light btn-lg calendly-trigger">Schedule a Consultation</a>
    </div>
